  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research is being done to study the ability of C. difficile to colonize the colonic&#xD;
      mucosa of individuals with no prior history of C. difficile infection.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The ability of C. difficile to colonize the mucosa of the colon will be studied in healthy&#xD;
      individuals with no history of C. difficile infection who are undergoing colonoscopy for&#xD;
      colon cancer/polyp screening purposes.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
